The paper discusses a security threat to Tor, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also extensively uses deep learning techniques to improve flow correlation attacks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the complex network of Tor, which falls under the category of networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the need for effective countermeasures, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SI). Finally, the paper discusses the implications of the threat to privacy, which falls under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CY).
